<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">غ ي ظ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْغَيْظُ)</span> غَضَبٌ كَامِنٌ لِلْعَاجِزِ.<span class="c5"> تَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">(غَاظَهُ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ بَاعَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(مَغِيظٌ)</span> وَلَا يُقَالُ: أَغَاظَهُ. وَ <span class="c2">(غَايَظَهُ فَاغْتَاظَ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(تَغَيَّظَ)</span> بِمَعْنًى.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>